span class=\"x-large\"><strong>港超聯｜飛馬成功爭取 24日對傑志回歸元朗上演</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n黎緊 24/3 星期三 元朗大球場 天水圍飛馬 對 傑志 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.sportsoho.com/pg/matchicon/8268213/original/default.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sportsoho.com%2Fpg%2Fmatchicon%2F8268213%2Foriginal%2Fdefault.jpg&h=1e362184&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"聽日<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">21號</span></span>元朗大球場有拖保費打比唔提埋？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:23:38.000Z","msg":"我已聚焦咗 24 個場, 聽日個場例行公事, 飛馬攞硬 3  分 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ba754f60e391847bb692c45bf01b9d30804eb0","tid":2454463,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a8dd1ef50088645950d10d7ee6e3298c072eae8","tid":2454463,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T09:08:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>【港超聯】旺角場再掛紅旗！三千人見證傑志東方和氣收場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3A_uZUTSAGtEbFrQY0iLiw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMC40O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/UpmEFZLbqFDLtucoNHPANw--~B/aD00MTc7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/7845b8471ef01fcac3cdf3e29f2417aa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3A_uZUTSAGtEbFrQY0iLiw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMC40O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FUpmEFZLbqFDLtucoNHPANw--~B%2FaD00MTc7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F7845b8471ef01fcac3cdf3e29f2417aa&h=1bc1b5b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【體路專訊】紅旗再高掛！港超聯今晚（19日）於旺角場上演「宿敵大戰」，由傑志主場迎戰東方龍獅。全場3000多張門票於開賽前50分鐘售罄，令在疫情下重開、座位減半的聯賽第二度掛上「爆棚」的紅旗，亦是繼2017年聯賽煞科戰後再次在旺角場有聯賽全場爆滿。傑志換邊後有丹恩奴域再在對方身上入球領先，但被艾華頓的「世界波」追和，最終在3101人見證下以各一言和。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/5Ax3U2FAHe9zUlyMnyRQTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC44O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/LHlAZ9la3owROGSOr8Sd2A--~B/aD01MzQ7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/ce357507d0db1a9f8ca248ea7e2fdb74\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F5Ax3U2FAHe9zUlyMnyRQTA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC44O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FLHlAZ9la3owROGSOr8Sd2A--~B%2FaD01MzQ7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fce357507d0db1a9f8ca248ea7e2fdb74&h=f1afb1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">下午已有數十名球迷在旺角場門外排隊。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/44jeH4rm65Y33TdJj0E8KQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/MbXgSMa7i6qzyzPKH2ntxw--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/332b0962d6cad79ed26911d98382a3b0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F44jeH4rm65Y33TdJj0E8KQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMbXgSMa7i6qzyzPKH2ntxw--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F332b0962d6cad79ed26911d98382a3b0&h=e75e008d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">即使旺角場6時許已經開閘，但排隊的球迷已遠至百米外的花墟徑。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/fsJb4Zqu7nHk15nECEF9Kw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/VxwCAqc0_fnrzsxT8SgNVA--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/7f53d4025d6884b01c8b04d44fdb5c72\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FfsJb4Zqu7nHk15nECEF9Kw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVxwCAqc0_fnrzsxT8SgNVA--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F7f53d4025d6884b01c8b04d44fdb5c72&h=cb8e202b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ctMNB9k0wlTUQSiqx6bCkg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Jx.7NUAmhPxcN28ImjMakA--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/a275d517108719d0223fa569b6b7ab13\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FctMNB9k0wlTUQSiqx6bCkg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FJx.7NUAmhPxcN28ImjMakA--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fa275d517108719d0223fa569b6b7ab13&h=3c559d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傑志及東方兩支宿敵10日內第二度對壘，雖然今仗缺少上場賽前球迷間的火藥味，但星期日傑志作客流浪「扯紅旗」，加上網上預售特惠票提早售罄，令這場今季第3次「傑東大戰」氣氛依然濃厚。傑志賽前兩日開放實體預售門票，截至昨日已售近1000張門票。到今日有球迷早在下午4時已開始在球場外排隊，隊尾在黃昏一度延伸至百米外的花墟徑。足總職員在開賽前50分鐘高掛紅旗，代表座位減半後的旺角場所有門票已經售罄。港超聯疫情前的最後一次「爆棚」已是2016至17球季煞科戰，對賽雙方同樣為傑志及東方。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nK0LQBvUhIbt9zyl88rO1w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/3pWjTtjyAKZyF6man.Qz3g--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/6ff78cd0786813bd94c0448a81ad76f4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnK0LQBvUhIbt9zyl88rO1w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3pWjTtjyAKZyF6man.Qz3g--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F6ff78cd0786813bd94c0448a81ad76f4&h=16218349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">丹恩奴域（左）上半場苦無表現。(渣架 !!) </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/54fSfuM9MfETsos1K.t9Ug--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/WA.FBP4CVUYYBn..wTrg5w--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/fc2f6f499cb954c7e9df47e6f2611f00\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F54fSfuM9MfETsos1K.t9Ug--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWA.FBP4CVUYYBn..wTrg5w--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Ffc2f6f499cb954c7e9df47e6f2611f00&h=b083a9be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">畢頓（中）完半場前的起腳甚具威脅。(咪又係無波入, 屌 !!)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/S5gcvXjSWz6ZaZZrA9X21w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Nt0DnXQQY8t1PZYaz9c3EA--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/679ff63a83a6c6f272e6ff1502eec435\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FS5gcvXjSWz6ZaZZrA9X21w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNt0DnXQQY8t1PZYaz9c3EA--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2F679ff63a83a6c6f272e6ff1502eec435&h=898bf026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"medium\">安永佳（中）失誤頻頻。(GYT GNHE !! )</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/7IQDHAcxwJ7jZ3Ct7eiedw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/g9CSbsiCQ_Cy9xs8wxyYCw--~B/aD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/en/sportsroad.hk/ca45f3c92869ba3711116dfebde6902f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F7IQDHAcxwJ7jZ3Ct7eiedw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzOS42O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fg9CSbsiCQ_Cy9xs8wxyYCw--~B%2FaD01MzM7dz04MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fsportsroad.hk%2Fca45f3c92869ba3711116dfebde6902f&h=f8ef7396&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩隊在之前兩次交手各勝一仗，賽果同樣是1：0僅勝。傑志今仗繼續派出巴爾拿及丹恩奴域兩名超級外援，後防則有丹尼、杜馬思、艾里奧及朴俊炯。東方的盧卡斯不入名單，費蘭度亦僅任後備，令前線的「巴西四寶」只餘艾華頓及辛祖，隊長梁振邦則續任正選與迪高夥拍中場。<br />\n<br />\n雖然這戰大戰氣氛濃厚，但上半場戰情卻是平平無奇。東方早段佔稍多控球，但辛祖及艾華頓始終未能突破傑志的防線。傑志前線更是誤傳頻頻，丹恩奴域、鄭展龍、安永佳及畢頓的默契明顯不足。全場首腳具威脅的射門要到29分鐘才出現，當時東方大打反擊，右翼李嘉耀單刀推順、無人看管下在禁區邊起腳被王振鵬接實。傑志就要到完半場前2分鐘才有畢頓禁區頂勁射被葉鴻輝撲出，門前的丹恩奴域未能補中。兩隊最終在打氣聲及場上偶爾的火藥味下互交白卷完半場。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:15:48.000Z","msg":"好多人呀！"},{"pid":"de44fb823f42c0d5f71247f6f5151345a9c2ac31","tid":2454463,"uid":296532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"想知邊度有提標題中FIFA果句？"},{"pid":"ea23cbd6d523e6741d582fb07505db98ba011913","tid":2454463,"uid":365380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"de44fb823f42c0d5f71247f6f5151345a9c2ac31","tid":2454463,"uid":296532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T14:54:21.000Z","msg":"想知邊度有提標題中FIFA果句？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:47:22.000Z","msg":"用你個名答返你自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11d70c59b1d6c0793059eec2db54aee93c40ba8d","tid":2454463,"uid":90422,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:51:09.000Z","msg":"原本以為會因為疫情再次進入冰河時期<br />\n可能真係冇晒娛樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入返場睇波"},{"pid":"0596af097360ee151c46cc5b7d0035e3b88c1d98","tid":2454463,"uid":9710,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"英超十二月前有段時間可以入場⋯⋯⋯"},{"pid":"72eaf69ce7b7e2452ce457e6b9e8f7da3bf5f7ff","tid":2454463,"uid":308251,"like":0,"disl